thread.title: Alisa Littau
thread.title_full: Medisave US LLP reviewed by Alisa Littau

author: Alisa Littau
title: Alisa Littau
text: I just received my Cardiology IV stethoscope, with engraving, and case. Products are excellent, service was very fast, and communication was great. I was notified the day after I placed my order that my items had shipped (wow!), and was notified when to expect delivery. I highly recommend Medisave and will shop with them again.
